Berlin IPFS/Blockstack Meetup at c-base - 2 June 2016

YouTube
Full, fixed HD video: youtu.be/CAfagNmIeOE IPFS Meetup is back in Berlin following the Decentralized and Encrypted conference! This time we will be seeing a continuation of the demos presented at D&E. 1) Introduction to IPFS and Blockstack (5 min Juan and Ryan Shea) 2) Introduction PLD Technical Deep Dive (10 min, Juan Benet) In this technical talk, Juan will walk through IPLD, the new standard for data on IPFS.
